attributionInfo.brokerName: EAGLE REAL ESTATE AND PROPERTY MANAGEMENT INC.

data.description: Welcome to this beautiful fully remodeled home with a large lot. This home features 2 Bedrooms 1 Vanity Bathrooms, ceiling fans, new closet doors.  Full Central A/C with upgraded kitchen, modern stove, modern stove, modern, hood , modern dishwasher, modern corian counters with a beautiful black design, modern windows.  This home also features a large lot and an (ADU) un-permitted back home with square footage not added and more than sufficient room for an RV with plenty of space to build a second home in the back and have animals.  Do not miss this opportunity to OWN this beautiful Ranch Style home.
